name: BRYLaunchExtension
summary: Integrate Beemray services in your app.
description:
Beemray help you accelerate your product with situational context. Enabling you to gain insights,
build new experiences, drive interactions, an engage in moments that really matter. Beemray automate
contextual intelligence using machine learning. We connect to the Adobe Experience Cloud, and the
rest of your tech partners. Everything takes place in real-time. This extension lets you use Beemray
features in your app.
